{"tid":739472,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"英撚球迷真係要收埋做","createTime":"2018-07-12T06:40:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-12T11:40:29.000Z","uid":75610,"like":13,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e98c1d05d0fc16a4f6db88db6b7a04650ef7251b","tid":739472,"uid":75610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T06:40:06.000Z","msg":"世界盃開始之前俾人笑出唔撚到線 <br />\n出到又有人笑16強過到哥倫比亞再講啦<br />\n入八強俾人笑贏到瑞典先算啦<br />\n四強諗住終於忍左咁耐有得打飛機 <br />\n點知心服口服輸經驗心態輸畀克羅地亞<br />\n<br />\n平時同朋友傾計都會屌返英撚幾句<br />\n因為睇咁多年都知道期望越大失望越大<br />\n買件波衫着都要笑下自己淨係着個三四場買黎做乜<br />\n唔講咁多希望有生之年見到英格蘭捧杯<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/12/143500_9773eb941668d72b8a881cc9fbe46d94.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F12%2F143500_9773eb941668d72b8a881cc9fbe46d94.png&h=a1a6b485&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/RJqimlFcJsM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRJqimlFcJsM&d=b%2BL7yZQHkTtw9lNrjqR4f0%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=e18edd3d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/RJqimlFcJsM</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br />\nThree Lions on the shirt<br />\n<br />\nJules Rimet still gleaming<br />\n<br />\nThirty years of hurt<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Never stopped me dreaming </span><br />\n<br />\nThree Lions on the shirt<br />\n<br />\nJules Rimet still gleaming<br />\n<br />\nThirty years of hurt<br />\n<br />\nNever stopped me dreaming<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\nSo many jokes, so many sneers<br />\n<br />\nBut all those oh-so-nears</span><br />\n<br />\nWear you down<br />\n<br />\nThrough the years</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/england.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/england.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/england.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nGod save the Queen"},{"pid":"c94b925e7db0c940cff74ba7ab7d5d0738f8dd42","tid":739472,"uid":144